    {
      "type": "explanation",
      "content": [
        { "type": "title", "value": "Hobbies" },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "To talk about what you like to do, use the verb <strong>鍾意</strong> (zung1 ji3 - to like). You can ask <strong>你鍾意做咩呀？</strong> (nei5 zung1 ji3 zou6 me1 aa3?) to find out about someone's hobbies."
        },
        {
          "type": "example",
          "cantonese": "鍾意",
          "romanization": "zung1 ji3",
          "translation": "To like"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Common hobbies include <strong>睇書</strong> (tai2 syu1 - reading books) and <strong>聽歌</strong> (teng1 go1 - listening to music/songs)."
        },
        {
          "type": "example",
          "cantonese": "睇書",
          "romanization": "tai2 syu1",
          "translation": "To read books"
        },
        {
          "type": "example",
          "cantonese": "聽歌",
          "romanization": "teng1 go1",
          "translation": "To listen to music"
        },
        {
          "type": "example",
          "cantonese": "嗜好",
          "romanization": "si3 hou3",
          "translation": "Hobbies"
        },
        {
          "type": "example",
          "cantonese": "旅遊",
          "romanization": "leoi5 jau4",
          "translation": "Traveling"
        }
      ]
    },
    { "type": "reading", "exerciseId": "3.4.2" },
    { "type": "unscramble", "exerciseId": "3.4.3" },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker": "A",
          "cantonese": "你鍾意做咩呀？",
          "romanization": "nei5 zung1 ji3 zou6 me1 aa3?",
          "translation": "What do you like to do?"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "B",
          "cantonese": "我鍾意睇書。你呢？",
          "romanization": "ngo5 zung1 ji3 tai2 syu1. nei5 ne1?",
          "translation": "I like reading books. What about you?"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "A",
          "cantonese": "我鍾意聽歌。",
          "romanization": "ngo5 zung1 ji3 teng1 go1.",
          "translation": "I like listening to music."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "B",
          "cantonese": "好呀。",
          "romanization": "hou2 aa3.",
          "translation": "Good."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker": "A",
          "cantonese": "黃先生，請問你平時有咩嗜好呢？",
          "romanization": "wong4 sin1 saang1, ceng2 man6 nei5 ping4 si4 jau5 me1 si3 hou3 ni1?",
          "translation": "Mr. Wong, may I ask what hobbies you usually have?"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "B",
          "cantonese": "我比較鍾意旅遊。",
          "romanization": "ngo5 bei2 gaau3 zung1 ji3 leoi5 jau4.",
          "translation": "I prefer traveling."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "A",
          "cantonese": "明白，多謝分享。",
          "romanization": "ming4 baak6, do1 ze6 fan2 hoeng2.",
          "translation": "Understood, thank you for sharing."
        }
      ]
    },
    { "type": "reading", "exerciseId": "3.4.4" },
